Modules Factory is pleased to announce the release of Piwik Web Analytic WHMCS Module v1.0. &lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Piwik is the leading open source web Analytic platform that gives you valuable insights into your website's visitors, your marketing campaigns and much more, so you can optimize your strategy and online experience of your visitors. Module allow you to sell Web Analytic services through your private piwik servers with auto provisioning and ability to control websites and tracking code from within client area.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;b&gt;Module Features:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fully Automated&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Limit Number of Websites/Service&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage Website in ClientArea&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;View Tracking Code in ClientArea&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Change Password&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Control Maximum number of Services per Server&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Choose User Email,password and Websites on Checkout&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multi-Language Support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
